Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不太慣海浪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:58.55,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\fad(500,400)\pos(1020,708)\bord0.3}「自行車」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 在外過夜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去不也有過喜歡的女孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的感觸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有除此以外的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都有點驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會喜歡上那樣天然的女孩倒是讓我吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說她壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不再需要我們就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不討厭你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx26\fry2\frz25.81\fs25\bord0\shad0\c&H80787E&\pos(432,274.666)}動物素描基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx26\fry2\frz25.81\fs30\bord0\shad1\c&H845575&\4c&HB79DBB&\fs28\pos(494.667,333.333)}第2章 從骨骼開始瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:02:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到的都是驅君的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透子 小柳來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小柳？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 現在練什麼項目？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50米自由式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前遊到32秒內了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標是在秋天之前進入31秒00
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小陽菜真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柳姐也在朝著夢想中的模特的工作努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直默默支持著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然身材好棒 真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次一起去買衣服什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你挑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 真的嗎 好的 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 透子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 突然跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外面聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小陽菜 再見囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於昨天雪君的事……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小柳那一巴掌……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得是驅君太過分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驅君嗎……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了行了 透子太好懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪……真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不明白他沒有贏面嗎 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎 幸今天住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說是住院檢查下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用那麼擔心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘量少去探望 別打擾到人家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可不能打擾墜入愛河的兩人幽會呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然小幸沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來發展良好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼沒什麼 我想去探望的話應該會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 那一會見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 最近大家都不怎麼聚過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從那個大衛出現以後感覺就不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可樂 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說醫院啊 探望時間很快就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不能想辦法拖到晚上十點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鋼琴家的握力真管用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,註：< 即為crescendo cresc. 漸強符號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.06,enf,,0000,0000,0000,,註：< 即為crescendo cresc. 漸強符號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,極強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.31,enf,,0000,0000,0000,,註：fff 即為fortissimo ff 非常強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那媽媽回去了 有什麼需要的就聯絡我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐君 男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我是幸的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我我我是幸的男朋友 叫白崎祐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是爺爺做的餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方居然有燕子的窩 一直都沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有雛鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是 確認到兩隻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺我明明一直住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驅君卻對這裡懂得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不太甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道這裡的各種瑣事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和透子一直生活在這裡的事實相比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 才沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驅君很厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像讓妳看到丟臉的一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天小柳來我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後聊了聊昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我和驅君 到底算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…突然就不能直接面對你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是保持超越了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同為持有奇怪能力的同伴這個關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛看到驅君掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要這樣待著就沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未來無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣比較安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天去海邊 說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也準時登場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啦 5點半的你～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人 是我姐姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識嗎 說過話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次都沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之他超帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像捲進麻煩的事裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,井美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教練
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有在繼續練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次的記錄賽 我看到你的時間都嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有啊 要是有什麼想商量的就來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 後天開始就是為期一週的夏季合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要找我的話就在那之前或之後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就好有幹勁呢 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽菜的社團活動也每天都有在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我昨天看到雪哉學長了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們泳池能看到他總在同一個時間跑過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不太明白是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過雪哉學長好像漸漸變成我們社團的偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們還吵著說要辦個粉絲會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界還真是小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為雪君很帥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度當然的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確呢 他跑起來很好看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 雪君很帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 為什麼這麼說 沒事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你說謊水準真是太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我去探望小幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也得趕緊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 馬上就要到今天檢查的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你每天來陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 那再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐……？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊這是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 我馬上就猜出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是祐君帶給妳的慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜對了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驅君？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是沖倉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 驅君他啊 說了些過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到那些話的小柳就……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 聽說明天也是個好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起看海是不是就能……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能發現些新的事物吧 我是這麼覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那些閃閃發亮的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得只要和驅君在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就漸漸地能明白那到底是什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我能再搞清楚點就來跟小幸妳報告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼了怎麼了 你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師要來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 我是深水透子的妹妹深水陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個 請別這麼不像樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 請不要消沉下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那難道不是未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎 小幸 這麼晚打電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天就出院了 下午大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想見見雪哉和小柳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上再一起放煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很突然 透子那邊就由我來聯絡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那我就去聯繫柳和雪哉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要喝什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我發簡訊問你去不去海邊 你沒回但能去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柳倒是回說能去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要跟女朋友去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成長為一個奇怪的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 我覺得是個很有魅力的男孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可無法想像這話會從孩子母親的嘴裡說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 之前那事 怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是檢查要延期一日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天才能出院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸 我昨天也跟你說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都給男朋友添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒有啦 麻煩什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了 那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 幸就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之得給他們發簡訊說今天不去了才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭大衛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這樣嗎 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人在的話 大家就會變得分崩離析
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確最近 大家都很難召集起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 妳打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天去海邊的行程要推到明天嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天透子跟大衛在日乃出的海濱約會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我從一開始就沒聯繫透子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳這意思不就成了…因為討厭大衛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家一起趕過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾透子跟大衛的約會 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我聯繫他們做這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小幸 你這意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天 就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz30.412\pos(698,606)\c&H3C2F2B&\bord0}抱歉 今天沒辦法去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 我知道了 我會告訴他的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是今天不去海邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到了嗎 今天不去海邊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒 我不討厭等人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然等很久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不習慣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海浪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟以前的感覺略有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是因為第一次在這個時間來大海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜻蜓玻璃球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一對的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透子說過的會摔下去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 所以絕對不能爬到高處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得這種事真的可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說誇張點 我今後這一生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒法攀登稍微有點可能會掉下去的地方了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼做才會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是未來的碎片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是 是驅君告訴我那是未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微想想會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去買飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驅君要什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候一直很納悶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大人要特意拿錢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去自動販賣機買水跟茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明旁邊還放著halpis water之類的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也叫了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透子沒和你一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才去買飲料了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 那趁這個機會現在跟你說聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪變得如此不堪都是因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打擾你們了 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是相配的一對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.77,0:23:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你好好解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別問了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透子 喂你怎麼了 看見什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想見見約拿單
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:40.07,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(211.2,435.2)\blur10\bord0.5}「雪」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
